[{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"CurrentModule = KhepriUnreal","category":"page"},{"location":"#KhepriUnreal","page":"Home","title":"KhepriUnreal","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"A Khepri backend for Unreal Engine, communicating via a C++ plugin over TCP (port 11010).","category":"page"},{"location":"#Architecture","page":"Home","title":"Architecture","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"KhepriUnreal is a SocketBackend using the :CPP (C++) binary protocol. It handles Unreal's left-handed coordinate system with an X-Y swap and 100x scale factor (Unreal uses centimeters).","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Backend type: SocketBackend{UEKey, Int}\nReference IDs: Int (Unreal actor/component IDs)\nCoordinate transform: X-Y swap with 100x scale â€” Khepri (x, y, z) becomes Unreal (y*100, x*100, z*100)\nCSG support: UEUnionRef and UESubtractionRef for boolean operations via BSP","category":"page"},{"location":"#Key-Features","page":"Home","title":"Key Features","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Material and resource families: UEMaterialFamily for material paths, UEResourceFamily for static mesh loading with parameter maps\nCSG via BSP: Boolean union and subtraction through Unreal's BSP system\nBIM elements: Walls, slabs, beams, panels, tables, chairs via InstantiateBIMElement\nFast mode: fast_unreal() for optimized bulk geometry transfer\nLighting: Point lights and spotlights with physically-based parameters","category":"page"},{"location":"#Setup","page":"Home","title":"Setup","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"using KhepriUnreal\nusing KhepriBase\n\nbackend(unreal)\n\nsphere(xyz(0, 0, 0), 5)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Requires Unreal Engine with the Khepri C++ plugin installed and listening on TCP port 11010.","category":"page"},{"location":"#Dependencies","page":"Home","title":"Dependencies","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"KhepriBase: Core Khepri functionality\nSockets: TCP communication","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Modules = [KhepriUnreal]","category":"page"}]
